Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal:\NPr/nc/pa/ vagina here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dan '1' let the name fool you.\NI'm very much in charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Reminding you that tonight is\Nour annual flu season dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many times\NI have to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you have the flu,\Nstay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The flu season dance is about\Nawareness, not celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't bring dead babies\Nto passover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Here we go.\NH-Hey, Jessica. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Um...\N- Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you about to talk...\NTo her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I mean, I was\Nthinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, stay in your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how hot she is.\NYou don't see me going...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To a bigger school\Nin a wealthier district
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and hitting on their\Nprettiest girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I throw balls far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You want good words?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Date a ianguager.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry:\NTry not to worry about it, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good kid,\Nand there's not a premium
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on that right now,\Nbut you'll be getting girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sometime after Brad's\Nout of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're missing the point, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want girls.\NI want Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, I remember\Nfeeling that way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,about a young lady named\N"your mom,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's not an urban diss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.66,0:01:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom was my Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the first time\NI saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought —-\N- "I should get her pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and then she'll have\Nto marry me."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon, Rick...\NInappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, please proceed\Nwith your story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about banging my daughter\Nin high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure you wanna take\Nromantic advice from this guy, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His marriage is hanging\Nfrom a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My marriage is fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry, it's your house...\NWhatever you say it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is how it is... but I think\Na blind man could see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that Beth is looking\Nfor the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely have a reason to care,\Nand even /noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rick! Don't talk\Nabout my parents like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, morty, I hate\Nto break it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but what people call "love"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is just a chemical reaction that\Ncompels animals to breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It hits hard, morty,\Nthen it slowly fades,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving you stranded\Nin a failing marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.\NYour parents are gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the cycle, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise above. Focus on science.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, well, I'm gonna go\Nget dressed for the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm just going to...\NCheck on your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, hand me\Nthat screwdriver, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost finished making\Nmy ionic defibulizer, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's gonna be great.\N- Hey, listen, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—y-you know how you said\Nthat, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,love is a chemical\Nand all that stuff from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was thinking, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,w-w... could you make some sort\Nof chemical thing happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,inside of Jessica's mind,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so where she falls in love\Nwith me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like, some sort\Nof love potion or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, that's such\Na poor use of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beneath me.\NHand me the screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? No, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna hand you\Nthe screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not gonna hand you\Nanything ever again, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always helping you with this\Nand that and the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-w—w-what about me, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-w—why can't you just\Nhelp me out once —-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,once —- for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing up fast, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing into a real big\NThorn straight up into my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, this is called oxytocin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I extracted it from a vole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what a vole is,\Nmorty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what a vole is?\NIt's a -— it's a rodent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that mates for life, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the chemical released\Nin a mammal's brain, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just gotta...\NCombine it with your DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A hair, morty.\NI need one of your hairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't "game of thrones."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, morty, whoever\Nyou smear this stuff on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,will fall in love with you,\Nand only you, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you happy now, morty?\N- Heck, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, grandpa Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's no...\NDangers or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or side effects, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-what am I, a hack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Go nuts, morty. It's foolproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, unless she has the flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Beth, do y-you still love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, what kind\Nof question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The "yes or no" kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry, do you want\Nhomeless people to have homes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna build them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what good was the "yes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, i-is loving me the house\Nor the homeless people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving you is work,\NJerry -— hard work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like building\Na homeless shelter -...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to say\Nno to doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but some people put the work in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?\NDo you see me working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this conversation seem\Ntedious to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I obviously\Nsort of love you, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop asking, and maybe\NI'll love you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, they need me\Nat the horse hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Puh! This late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The racetrack\Nhad a starlight derby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a seven-horse\Ncollision,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and Davin's there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Davin. Davin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vin! Da vin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vin! Da vin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Da vin! Da vin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,J” flu, yo. You gotta be aware j“
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,j” aware of all the flu\Nup in the air j”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,j” I'm-a get me a shot,\Nmake the flu go away j”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,j” flu-hating rapper,\Njust rapping away j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,j” yo, yo, flu-hating rapper j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,j” it's a flu-hating rap j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,hey, there, Jessica.\NWhoa! Oh, whoopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god. Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You look really nice tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow, thanks.\N- I love you, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much it burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!\NI-I love you too, Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this punk bothering you,\NJessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone, jerk!\NI'm in love with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He is more man\Nthan you will ever be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,J” this is about flu awareness j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,j” gotta be aware of the flu\Nin the air-ness j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,j” yo, I'm a flu-hating\Nrapper j”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, man, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, n-no problem, Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something special\Nabout you, morty —-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, take it easy!\NGet your hands off of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!\NI'm trying to be with my man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want you injuring\Nyour ball-throwing arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on,\Nprincipal vagina. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Never leave me, morty. Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.\NI mean, o—of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do you think that\Nwas all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Just hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I love you, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry: She's gonna be alone\Nwith that guy all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, dad, digging\Naround the insides of horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a very romantic setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick: Well, summer,\Nthere's always the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that she made the whole\Nwork thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Davin's digging around\Nin herinsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, so gross!\NYou're talking about my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's my daughter, summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or family means nothing, in\Nwhich case don't play that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not responding\Nto my texts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, dad.\NJealousy turns women off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for the men\Nthey cheat on, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm... going to go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For some ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe\Nstop by the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To support my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,God, grandpa,\Nyou're such a dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, summer. Your opinion\Nmeans very little to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're not at this\Nstupid dance everyone loves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that.\NI don't wanna get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's flu season.\N- It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just let this work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, morty. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip my clothes off\Nand mate with me for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... can we maybe go\Nsomewhere more private?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't deserve to carry\Nmorty's genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,J” I love morty j”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,j” and I hope morty loves me j”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,j” I'd like to wrap my arms\Naround him j”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,j” and feel him inside me j”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jessica: Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, come on!\NWe gotta get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't believe this 'cause\Nit usually never happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, morty.\NWe got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on.\N- Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Morty: - Vagina: Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm fine!\N- Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything ever happened to\Nyou, I would kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you bad, mo—mo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty, the principal and I\Nhave discussed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a-a-and we're both insecure\Nenough to agree to a three-way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize\Nwhen I gave you that serum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that Jessica had the flu...\NYou know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,t-t-t—t-t-that might have been\Nvaluable information for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,T-t-t-the serum is\Npiggybacking on the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone airborne, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap.\NWhat are we gonna do, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine,\Nmorty, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I whipped up an antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's based on praying-mantis\NDNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, praying mantises\Nare the exact opposite of voles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they... they mate once,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they, you know,\Ndecapitate the partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's a whole ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really gruesome\Nand totally opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no love at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I basically mixed this with\Na more contagious flu virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It should neutralize\Nthe whole thing, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all be over very shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, by the way, morty, I know\Nyou didn't ask or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not interested\Nin having sex with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These serums, they don't\Nwork on anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,related to you genetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,science is more art\Nthan science, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people don't get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[Gasdsi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello!\N- Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not morty!\NBring us morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until after I catch my wife\Nwith another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman on TV:\N/hao' sex with Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman #2:\NBut you were already pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what's the worst\Nthat could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We interrupt "pregnant bab y”\Nwith breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This just in... ll/lorty Smith is\Nwhereabouts are still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that is known\Nis... how cute he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him so much, / want\Nto make love to him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then eat his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,//o ve him more than you do,\NHarold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish, you stupid bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Li/lorty's mine!\N- Ll/lorty's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meant to be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ll/lorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god, Rick.\NThe whole world is infected!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty wild\Nhow fast that spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've really outdone myself.\N- Outdone yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W... a—are -— are you\Nkidding me, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only do they all want\Nto have sex with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but, you know, now they want\Nto eat me aftennards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know what\NI was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantises are\Nthe opposite of voles?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, obviously, DNA's more\Ncomplicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, though, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This right here's gonna do\Nthe trick, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's koala mixed\Nwith rattlesnake, chimpanzee,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cactus, shark, golden retriever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and just a smidge of dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Should add up\Nto normal humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... that doesn't make\Nany sense, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that add up\Nto normal humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What, morty, you want me\Nto show you my math?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry -— a-are you\Nthe scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or are you the kid\Nthat wanted to get laid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad we saved\Nall those horses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm almost sorry\Nwe're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's satisfying work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unh-unh-unh, it's, uh...\NIt's more than the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I love being\Nin that sterilized room,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sealed off from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only time I can\Nreally think... and feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, uh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing African dream pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do\Nafter a long night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ha, um, hey, I b...\NI'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Jerry's been texting some\Npretty high-maintenance stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Beth...\N- What is it, Davin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once, I'd like to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What it was like\Nto give your son a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What does morty's skin\Nsmell like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How soft are his privates?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Davin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Mr. Crowbar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,who is also a crowbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look where being\Nsmart got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerry! Thank god!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God's turning people\Ninto insect monsters, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one beating them\Nto death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank me.\N- Thank you, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look down there,\Nmorty, and soak it in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because, you know,\Nonce I pull this lever,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, technically,\Nmorty, there's no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know,\No-once it's fixed, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fixed.\NYou know, we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We could just enjoy it\Nfor a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, i-i-i-look\Nat how crazy it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, morty,\Nw-w-when's the next time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna see\Nsomething like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, soak it in, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's pretty neat.\NIt's pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Rick!\NI'm pulling the lever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What do we have here, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I was right\Nand you were wrong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I—I—i-i bet you feel pretty\Nstupid right about now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I—I bet you feel like\Nthe world's smallest man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you were doubting me about\Nthis whole thing, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rick, something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not right... ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! Look, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you're loving this, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the best day\Nof your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to be the mayor\Nof i-told-you town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that shotgun\Nwas my penis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were, you could\Ncall me Ernest Hemingway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it,\Nand I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer: Mom! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think grandpa Rick had\Nsomething to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair to\Nassume that, summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not fair? Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a selfish,\Nirresponsible ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and he left my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A real man stands by his woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,J” tchoo. Tchoo-tchoo-tchoo.\NTchoo-tchoo j”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,boy, I really cronenberged\Nthe world up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a whole planet of\Ncronenbergs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,walking around\Ndown there, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A—at least they're not in love\Nwith you anymore, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a huge step\Nin the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god!\NIt's a living nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you be\Nso irresponsible, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me irresponsible?! You...\NAll I wanted you to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was hand me\Na screwdriver, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who wanted to\Nbe... wanted me to buckle down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and make you up a...\NRoofie-juice serum
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so you could roofie that\Npoor girl at your school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, g... w-w-w-w-w... w...\NAre you kidding me, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna try to take\Nthe high road on this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-y-y-y-you're a little\Ncreep, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—you're a... you're...\NYou're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a little creepy...\NCreep person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine. I should have\Njust listened to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,when you refused to make\Nthe serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to accept my part of\Nthe blame for this, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you something...\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta accept your part\Nof the blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one\Nwho fouled up the serum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who -—\NWho... who...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who haphazardly, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,mixed a bunch of nonsense\Ntogether
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and created a bunch of\Ncronenbergs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- You gotta fix this, Rick!\N- All right, all right, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, w-w-w-we are\Nin a pretty deep hole, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I do have one emergency\Nsolution that I can use
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll kind of put\Neverything back to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,relatively speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, morty, put this on\Nwhile I do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit of scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Morty: Wow, Rick, I gotta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really pulled a rabbit out\Nof your hat this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I-I really thought\Nthat the whole place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was gonna be messed up for good,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but here, you did it -—\NY-y—you " you '-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you figured out that crazy\Nsolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! That's some great luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, morty. Luck had\Nnothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great.\NThat's the real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, morty, what do you\Nsay, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you hand me a screwdriver
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can finish my ionic\Ndis... defibulizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Rick.\NHere's a screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, morty.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We got one screw turn...\NAnd two screw turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, morty, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god, Rick! Is that us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-we're dead!\NWhat is going on, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, morty!\NLook at me! Calm down, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deal with this, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Calm down, morty.\N- This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You gotta calm down, morty.\N- W-W—w—w-we're ripped apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an infinite number\Nof realities, morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and in a few dozen of those,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lucky and turned\Neverything back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had to find one\Nof those realities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we also happen to both\Ndie around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can just slip\Ninto the place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of our dead selves\Nin this reality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not skipping a beat,\Nmorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, help me with these bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, morty, I'll grab myself,\Nyou grab yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, t-t-t-that seems\Nfair to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that seems like\Na fair way to divvy it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick, what about\Nthe reality we left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the reality where\NHitler cured cancer, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is don't\Nthink about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we can do this\Nevery week, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We get three or four more\Nof these, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pick up your dead self\Nand come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Haste makes waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I—I don't suppose you've\Nconsidered this detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but obviously, if! Hadn't\Nscrewed up as much as I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd be these guys right now,\Nso, again, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,J” look on down\Nfrom the bridge j”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,j” there's still fountains\Ndown there j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,j” look on down\Nfrom the bridge j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,j” it's still raining up here j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,j” everybody seems so far away\Nfrom me j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,j” everybody just wants\Nto be free j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,j” look away from the sky j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,j” it's no different\Nwhen you're leaving home j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,j” I can't be the same thing\Nto you now j”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,j” I'm just gone j”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,j” just gone j”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,j” how could I say goodbye? J”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,j” how could I say goodbye? J”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, the thing\Nabout a shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got lifeless eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Black eyes, like a doll's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When he comes at ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't seem to be living\Nuntil he bites ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the -— the blood,\Nand the red, and the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever wonder what happened\Nto Rick and morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes.\NBut, I'm ashamed to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,now that they're gone,\NI'm finally happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are, cronenberg morty —-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a reality where\Neveryone in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,got genetically cronenberged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fit right in,\Ncronenberg morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be like we never even\Nleft cronenberg world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, cronenberg Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but, you know, I'm gonna miss\Ncronenberg world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone\Nwas cronenberged all along
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,like us from the beginning,\Nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I-I wish we hadn't\Ngenetically ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,cronenberg world\Nbeyond repair like we did,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, and turned everyone\Ninto regular, normal people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,just walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about\Nthat sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,cronenberg morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go make ourselves\Nat home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good-a show!
